</head>

<body>



<!-- HERO SECTION -->
<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
        <h1>WHAT IS ASME?</h1>
        <p>
            The American Society of Mechanical Engineers (ASME) is a global
            professional organization dedicated to advancing engineering,
            fostering collaboration, and promoting innovation worldwide.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT GLOBAL ASME -->
<section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>About ASME</h2>

        <p>
            Founded in 1880, ASME is an international organization that
            promotes the art, science, and practice of multidisciplinary
            engineering and allied sciences around the globe.
        </p>

        <p>
            With members in over 140 countries, ASME develops globally
            recognized engineering standards, organizes conferences,
            publishes technical research, and connects engineers across
            academia and industry.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT ASME DOES -->
<section class="content-section dark">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>What Does ASME Do?</h2>

        <div class="grid-3">

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Standards & Codes</h3>
                <p>
                    ASME develops internationally recognized standards that
                    ensure safety, reliability, and efficiency across
                    industries including energy, manufacturing, and aerospace.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Technical Conferences</h3>
                <p>
                    It hosts global conferences and competitions that bring
                    engineers together to exchange ideas, present research,
                    and showcase innovation.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Student Development</h3>
                <p>
                    ASME empowers students through design challenges,
                    leadership programs, networking opportunities,
                    and professional growth initiatives.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ASME AT BITS -->
<section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>ASME at BITS Pilani</h2>

        <p>
            ASME BITS Pilani is a student-led chapter committed to fostering
            technical excellence, innovation, and leadership among engineering
            students.
        </p>

        <p>
            Through workshops, technical competitions, industrial
            collaborations, and hands-on projects, we provide students with
            real-world engineering exposure and professional development.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- IMPACT / STATS -->
